snippet.description:

Guest Speaker, Amber Fleming, Senior Financial Services Advisor at State Employees' Credit Union shared details on how a credit union differs from a regular bank, services that they can provide, eligibility requirements, and a general update on how the organization is currently operating during the COVID-19 pandemic. We also briefly heard from SECU Senior Vice President, Lilnette Phillips.

snippet.title: DipIt #14: Mosquito in Amber Prop Replica
snippet.description:
This is a prop replica of the amber cane John Hammond used in the movie Jurassic Park! My portion was the completion of the amber topper!

It came out amazing. We are now one step closer to cloning a dinosaur!
